{"tid":2098132,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"快啲入嚟多謝公務員手足！","createTime":"2020-07-07T09:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T09:38:31.000Z","uid":362414,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba26425004dc9d21b1c88b7404788028ca8faaec","tid":2098132,"uid":362414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:11:09.000Z","msg":"有做緊政府嘅friend爆料: 參與整健康健康碼計劃嘅公務員手足喺背後做咗唔少嘢。手足知道<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一旦健康碼推出，成班大陸人又會沖入香港</strong></span>！因此手足用盡各種方法頂住上頭，拖得就拖，次次阿頭問起就話有傳播風險考慮或者系統唔穩定。 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">本來今個禮拜已經頂唔住</span></strong>，點知今日疫情大爆發！ 天助手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 照睇可以拖多幾個月唔使畀啲大陸人沖入香港。住內地嘅藍絲九月都唔使旨意返嚟投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家快啲多謝前線公務員手足！大灣區收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持永遠封關！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP牌推唔到"},{"pid":"a440bd59822973a33cd9f0c993846056f80f45e8","tid":2098132,"uid":10990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde70859774c25a20b5ef8bf95eb8d0922d26d36","tid":2098132,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:13:01.000Z","msg":"應該要一早爆出嚟"},{"pid":"d6c7342cffe9fcb75f51129f7ca9d1b83557123d","tid":2098132,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:14:59.000Z","msg":"你都幾好笑，健康碼唔推出就無大陸人沖入香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb18632c11807262b846add9cc6143d228167382","tid":2098132,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:17:32.000Z","msg":"唔係好明"},{"pid":"d1a2c5e56e4f5c66439bead6c2bbf9bb27a93215","tid":2098132,"uid":362414,"lik